  "intent": "Execute a 4-point drug dilution assay starting from 200\u00b5M stock concentration. First, dispense 100\u00b5L of Media+IL-2+OKT3+CD28 to all wells across three 96-well plates (0.1\u00b5M, 1\u00b5M, 10\u00b5M final concentrations). Perform serial 10-fold dilutions by transferring 10\u00b5L between plates: 200\u00b5M stock \u2192 10\u00b5M plate \u2192 1\u00b5M plate \u2192 0.1\u00b5M plate, with 4x mixing at 10\u00b5L before initial transfer and 4x mixing at 10\u00b5L after each transfer step. Discard final 10\u00b5L to waste. Complete by adding 100\u00b5L cell suspension to all wells with 5x mixing at 300\u00b5L before each transfer.",
